33 struct HandleMsgReturn
34 {
35  static constexpr int max_failures = 200;
36 
37  static bool getCorrectMsg(const end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatusConstPtr &data, int value)
38  {
39  bool data_received = false;
40  for (int i = 0; i < max_failures; i++)
41  {
42  if (data && data->action == value)
43  {
44  data_received = true;
45  break;
46  }
47 
48  ros::spinOnce();
49  ros::WallDuration(0.01).sleep();
50  }
51  return data_received;
52  }
53 
54  template <class T> static bool publisherIsOn(const boost::shared_ptr<T const> &data)
55  {
56  bool data_received = false;
57  for (int i = 0; i < max_failures; i++)
58  {
59  if (data)
60  {
61  data_received = true;
62  break;
63  }
64  else
65  {
66  ros::spinOnce();
67  ros::WallDuration(0.01).sleep();
68  }
69  }
70  return data_received;
71  }
72 };
73 // Test service set Digital IO
74 TEST(EndEffectorTestTSuite, serviceTest)
75 {
76  auto client = nh->serviceClient<end_effector_interface::SetEEDigitalOut>("end_effector_interface/set_ee_io_state");
77 
78  // wait for node launched
79  bool exists(client.waitForExistence(ros::Duration(10.0)));
80  EXPECT_TRUE(exists);
81 
82  end_effector_interface::SetEEDigitalOut srv;
83  client.call(srv);
84 
85  EXPECT_EQ(srv.response.state, true);
86 }

88 // check if status of button from driver is published to upper layer or not
89 // in real hw, we can't check because of manually press on button.
90 TEST(EndEffectorTestSuite, publisherTestButtonCustom)
91 {
92  end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatusConstPtr data;
93  ros::Subscriber sub = nh->subscribe<end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatus>("end_effector_interface/custom_button_status", 10,
94  [&data](const end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatusConstPtr msg) { data = msg; });
95 
96  // wait a while to get data from topic
97  bool res = HandleMsgReturn::getCorrectMsg(data, 0);
98 
99  ASSERT_EQ(sub.getNumPublishers(), 1U);
100 
101  ASSERT_TRUE(res) << "No data sent from publisher on topic end_effector_interface/custom_button_status";
102 
103  EXPECT_EQ(data->action, 0);
104 }
